title: INCREDIBLE MARINA VIEWS AVAILABLE IN THIS 1BR/1BA ApT. with A BALCONY
posting_body: ['Dolphin Marina Monte Carlo', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', '1 \xa0bedroom 1 bath 708Sq.', 'Ft.  $2,945/mo', 'Finest Waterside Living in Marina Del Rey', 'Dolphin Marina Monte Carlo Apartments presents this one-bedroom, one-bathroom home with a fireplace and central heating and cooling.', 'The apartment has floor-to-ceiling windows and a large soaking tub.', 'The stylish kitchen has a built-in stove so you can prepare your favorite dishes anytime.', 'The home also includes wirings for high-speed Internet, and some homes also have walk-in closets.', 'Select a residence that offers a balcony with an incredible view of the marina!', 'Dolphin Marina Monte Carlo has great amenities for relaxation, such as a spa, a heated pool, and a sauna.', 'Residents can go to the twenty-four-hour fitness center or the yoga studio to de-stress.', 'This pet-friendly community is on the water in Marina Del Rey and is close to shops and restaurants.', 'Call now.', 'PROPERTY AMENITIES:', '*', 'FitnessCenter', '* Courtesy Patrol', '* Recreation Room W/ Kitchen', '* Reserved Gated Parking', '* Spa', 'MANAGED BY:', 'GK MANAGEMENT CO INC**', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'Address:', '13970 Panay Way Marina Del Rey, CA 90292', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
